                     <interp inst="t17920329-1-person53" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>Corroborated the testimony of the last witness.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17920329-1-verdict4" type="verdictDescription">
